{"tid":2233411,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫台慶連出兩部警察劇  Stephy、MIRROR《男排女將》幫ViuTV迎戰《使徒3》","createTime":"2020-10-07T06:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T08:17:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21e1c05fdee55fa12f93ad0bca5ecc7809a7d2ab","tid":2233411,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201006/6VMD6O6RUJF57NQVKN7BO3QBQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201006%2F6VMD6O6RUJF57NQVKN7BO3QBQQ%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=37798368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201006%2F6VMD6O6RUJF57NQVKN7BO3QBQQ%2F&h=8e3ec76f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201006/6VMD6O6RUJF57NQVKN7BO3QBQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n無綫台慶連出兩部警察劇 <br />\nStephy、MIRROR《男排女將》幫ViuTV迎戰《使徒3》<br />\n<br />\n當警隊民望跌至歷史低點，無綫下月將推出由羅仲謙及林峯分別主演的警察劇《木棘証人》及《使徒行者3》作台慶劇，似想為警隊挽回形象。ViuTV有見及此也嚴陣以待，近日公佈將安排鄭中基的《暖男爸爸》及鄧麗欣（Stephy）與MIRROR成員主演的《男排女將》出戰對撼，《男》劇更要正面迎戰「爆Seed」林峯的回巢作，不過Stephy依然對新劇更充滿信心及期待。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【破格綜藝】《造星III》藝人參賽博反彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4S5wvHryA4tnb4plGP4wRchgeJg=/640x477/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KSO5TNPPJ5FNBL45RLMD3B736M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4S5wvHryA4tnb4plGP4wRchgeJg%3D%2F640x477%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKSO5TNPPJ5FNBL45RLMD3B736M.jpg&h=03e056e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Stephy新劇《男排女將》將為ViuTV迎戰無綫台慶劇，她期待劇集播出外，也希望令更多人喜歡排球。劇照<br />\n<br />\n今年ViuTV播出的自家劇集《二月廿九》、《歎息橋》及《地產仔》等成功掀起不少熱話，口碑及收視皆不俗，為他們打下強心針，。。。。。。。。。。。。ViuTV未敢掉以輕心，近日公佈已安排由電影《龍咁威》組合，鄧麗欣及鄭中基分別主演的《男排女將》和《暖男爸爸》迎戰，正面交鋒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UENqBASCYboIkyMButHz4ElouyQ=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/44CI5GTCMBAU5OPLA2ZS6Z5OWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUENqBASCYboIkyMButHz4ElouyQ%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F44CI5GTCMBAU5OPLA2ZS6Z5OWM.jpg&h=98fcf4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《男排女將》除了MIRROR成員陳卓賢、柳應廷及邱傲然等演出外，還有新生代演員顧定軒。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AACFjvAc-yo90dkm-XjDtP03uMU=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P2BX5I42C5DD3KSLIAWRK3WLXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAACFjvAc-yo90dkm-XjDtP03uMU%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP2BX5I42C5DD3KSLIAWRK3WLXM.jpg&h=287af416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Stephy在2015年成立Loey排球隊，更曾參與香港的公開賽。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nTHnKKqOWXK5_94FOYXXUVmFMmI=/640x1555/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CO7IQTFCCBBBNC4PZJFY6QQW2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnTHnKKqOWXK5_94FOYXXUVmFMmI%3D%2F640x1555%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCO7IQTFCCBBBNC4PZJFY6QQW2Y.jpg&h=de9faa0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Ian同樣是排球健將，曾入選香港男子排球代表隊。 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n排球健將添說服力<br />\n<br />\nStephy主演的《男》劇講述一班熱愛排球的青年因身高未達標而被放棄，但後來遇上Stephy飾演的前排球代表隊成員，眾青年喚醒她的熱誠，因此令她組成一支男子排球隊及擔任教練。劇集除了Stephy演教練外，一班男排隊成員則由MIRROR成員陳卓賢（Ian）、盧瀚霆（Anson Lo）、柳應廷（Jeremy）及Error成員梁業（肥仔）和郭嘉駿（193）等演出。現實中Stephy及Ian不約而同入行前也是排球健將，Ian更曾是香港男排隊代表，兩人的演出相信會更有說服力。《男》劇將於下月23日播出，正正對戰下月16日首播的《使徒3》。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：與傅穎禮物傳情破冰<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。；而《男》劇則是香港鮮有的排球劇，加上有人氣高企的MIRROR及ERROR成員，ViuTV今次或能成功突圍而出。<br />\n<br />\n對於新劇對撼《使3》，Stephy昨日回覆《蘋果》時表示：「我一直都想拍排球題材，所以好享受成個過程，同同劇嘅年輕演員合作得非常開心，我都好期待套劇最後呈現出嚟嘅效果。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JVKQCgsdALVy9iC6FcHg0TzI6CQ=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GGBQHJX625AEJBILWULNXALFCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJVKQCgsdALVy9iC6FcHg0TzI6CQ%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGGBQHJX625AEJBILWULNXALFCU.jpg&h=990bdddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■無綫《使徒3》有久未拍港劇的林峯（左），與難得演大反派的馬國明。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rt7ncoYwudyMIc0lmT77WZMrhYg=/640x491/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H4TMIYHLVRCUXCOCIGSDKFKOQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Frt7ncoYwudyMIc0lmT77WZMrhYg%3D%2F640x491%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH4TMIYHLVRCUXCOCIGSDKFKOQE.jpg&h=5ea5dcf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭中基在《暖男爸爸》不搞笑，反而走溫情路線。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《暖男爸爸》月底播<br />\n<br />\n由鄭中基及張可頤主演的《暖》劇則在本月26日出街，24日將率先播製作特輯造勢，羅仲謙的《木》劇則在本月19日推出，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。不少網民近日在討論區議論紛紛，有不少人留言會力撐ViuTV：「有冇鄭中基同Stephy都唔重要，最重要係反CCTVB。」、「黃唔黃我唔知，但係佢哋都拍港產片就like。」"},{"pid":"721c17cc0873c3070f5005ad6dcc1203169dfcdc","tid":2233411,"uid":68689,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4060686/org/57a96918d87a0f2cad5a28f73d8ed423.jpg/lcsYTNW2gZCMzXsR3TQmDNnR725KTxfk6id-a-onfms?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4060686%2Forg%2F57a96918d87a0f2cad5a28f73d8ed423.jpg%2FlcsYTNW2gZCMzXsR3TQmDNnR725KTxfk6id-a-onfms%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3c5eeb45&s={SIZE}\" />"